title: Unsolved NFL Mysteries
itunes:title: Unsolved NFL Mysteries
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – are joined by NFL Network’s Dan Hellie as they break down the latest NFL news including Von Miller’s comments regarding his contract situation and the chances Andy Dalton will become an elite QB. Then the heroes dive into some “Unsolved NFL Mysteries” before ending the podcast sharing some great summer songs.
